John Hargrove was a trainer at SeaWorld for 14 years . 
  Last week he released a book criticizing the company's treatment of animals . 
  SeaWorld has released a video of him using the N-word seven times while talking on the phone with a female friend . 
  The trainer says SeaWorld is mounting a smear campaign against him . 
  In the video he discusses an incident in which five black men allegedly threw a rock at a friend . 
  He was a star of the documentary Blackfish and was a SeaWorld trainer for 15 years . 
  The video comes just days after he released his book about his time at the park . 
 